---

## âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone and Install

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Akshat_Saxena/fastapi-ecommerce
cd fastapi-ecommerce
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # or venv\Scripts\activate on Windows
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Setup `.env`

```env
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:yourpass@localhost:5432/ecommerce_db
SECRET_KEY=your_jwt_secret
ALGORITHM=HS256

EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
EMAIL_PORT=587
EMAIL_USER=yourgmail@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your_app_password
```

### 3. Run Alembic Migrations

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### 4. Run the Server

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

Visit: [http://localhost:8000/docs](http://localhost:8000/docs)

---

## ğŸ“« Reset Password Flow

1. `POST /auth/forgot-password` with email â†’ sends reset token
2. `POST /auth/reset-password` with token + new password

---

## âœ… Admin vs User Permissions

| Action               | User | Admin |
| -------------------- | ---- | ----- |
| Sign Up / Login      | âœ…    | âœ…     |
| Access JWT Routes    | âœ…    | âœ…     |
| View Products        | âœ…    | âœ…     |
| Create/Edit Products | âŒ    | âœ…     |
| Use Cart             | âœ…    | âŒ     |
| Checkout + Orders    | âœ…    | âŒ     |

